se leading-relaxed text-neutral-600","children":[[["$","p","0",{"children":"Whatever support you need, our experienced caregivers will share in your interests and accompany you in whatever you like to do whether that is crafting, going for a walk, playing games or enjoying music. Naptec day care is flexible to fit in with you. You might only want a few hours or a full day of support and whatever you need, we will match you with a caregiver who will become a trusted companion who enables you to continue living a fulfilled and active life."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Naptec day care at home is also ideal for people living with dementia, Parkinson's or for those recovering from a stroke or enduring a mental health need such as depression."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"Day care:"}]],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc space-y-2 pl-5","children":[["$","li","Is personalised to you",{"children":"Is personalised to you"}],["$","li","Promotes a stimulating and active lifestyle",{"children":"Promotes a stimulating and active lifestyle"}],["$","li","Is flexible to meet your needs",{"children":"Is flexible to meet your needs"}],["$","li","Gives peace of mind that your loved one is safe at home",{"children":"Gives peace of mind that your loved one is safe at home"}],["$","li","Helps families take a rest from caring",{"children":"Helps families take a rest from caring"}],["$","li","Is specialised and expert",{"children":"Is specialised and expert"}]]}],null,null]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"relative aspect-[4/3] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-sm bg-[#f2f2f2] ","children":["$","$L13",null,{"src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dw1n6qugv/image/upload/v1778932857/centre-for-ageing-better-rQJ3xo-0WYE-unsplash_mhe64i.jpg","alt":"Day care at home","fill":true,"sizes":"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 50vw","className":"object-cover"}]}]]}],["$","div","What can I expect from Naptec day care?",{"className":"mx-auto mt-14 grid max-w-6xl gap-8 sm:mt-16 lg:mt-20 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-cent